{"tid":1206217,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘站 警逼年輕人一字排開靠牆搜查","createTime":"2019-06-12T02:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T02:03:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eba54deb6b32db87fad49345c7dfa32f582d3a0b","tid":1206217,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:00:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tnimage.s3.hicloud.net.tw/photos/2019/06/12/1560303604-5d0057f4260a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftnimage.s3.hicloud.net.tw%2Fphotos%2F2019%2F06%2F12%2F1560303604-5d0057f4260a7.jpg&h=2b3cc663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(毛孟靜臉書)<br />\n<br />\n昨（11日）晚19時香港警察在金鐘站（鄰近立法會、政府總部的地鐵站）截查市民，竟要求被查民眾一字排開靠牆搜查，引發路過市民不滿。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱因應網上有人稱將攜帶危險工具到示威區，故在金鐘一帶嚴加搜查戴口罩或攜背包的市民。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港議員毛孟靜昨夜於Facebook的貼文，警方將年輕人市民逼到牆邊「罰站」，一字排開搜查身分證，而查完身分證後卻又不立刻放行。有民眾看不過，上前「幫腔」與警察理論，也隨即遭警察盤問。<br />\n<br />\n根據毛孟靜所述，被搜查的人當中，大半是準備前往政府總部前參加祈禱會的基督徒，部分則是因為和警察理論而遭盤問的市民。<br />\n<br />\n根據港媒《明報》報導，有市民只因帶三瓶礦泉水，被警方以髒話辱罵質問。<br />\n<br />\n現場一度引來200人圍觀，有人批評港警「製造白色恐怖」。網民也大力撻伐，指警方「助紂為虐」、「黑警」等。<br />\n<br />\n警員於21時左右離開，現場民眾大喝倒采，許多人更將搜查全程以手機錄影存證。<br />\n<br />\n然而，議員毛孟靜稱制服警員雖然收隊撤離，卻隨即換成便服回到現場，批評警方作法「奸詐」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/ch/news/3722251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwannews.com.tw%2Fch%2Fnews%2F3722251&d=Q0Uk0WlElUZ8hxv%2Fjb96J%2F56hpy2SSQtx6ElJ%2BvIbMI%3D&h=b08af407\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/ch/news/3722251</a>"},{"pid":"82bc244f01d9907e8ac07c1de988387dd61d1c95","tid":1206217,"uid":22360,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:00:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母old news"},{"pid":"5ca0156c489d6e4bea088f8db9ffe2ce6882e558","tid":1206217,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8cb0744913b47c21897d9e84370c533d36113ca","tid":1206217,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:01:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">法西斯</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"74893f59733f96969006d098a1db6124932d78df","tid":1206217,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82bc244f01d9907e8ac07c1de988387dd61d1c95","tid":1206217,"uid":22360,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:00:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母old news"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T02:03:30.000Z","msg":"... is so ex西ting<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}